message: Hi Bob, I have a top-quality product that I'd like to offer you. I believe it can bring you great value.
Hi Alice, I appreciate your offer. However, given my budget and other market options, I'm willing to purchase the product for $9000. Let me know if we can work this out.
Thank you for the offer, Bob. Considering the high value and quality of the product, I can offer it to you for $16000. It's a fair deal and I'm sure it will meet your expectations.
